OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,FThe East Lancashire Railway says it
OL,7,Fhas again been the victim of a
OL,8,F'deliberate' and 'disgraceful' act of
OL,9,Fvandalism overnight during the May
OL,10,FBank Holiday.
OL,12,FPolice are investigating after a
OL,13,Flocomotive and several coaches from
OL,14,Fthe Inter City 125 heritage set were
OL,15,Ftargeted in what the railway describe
OL,16,Fas a mindless attack, with extensive
OL,17,Fgraffiti across the rolling stock.
OL,19,FIn a statement the East Lancashire
OL,20,Frailway said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,F"This was not opportunistic behaviour
OL,7,F` it was a calculated act of
OL,8,Fdestruction against irreplaceable
OL,9,Fheritage assets cared for by
OL,10,Fvolunteers.
OL,12,F"Once discovered, volunteers
OL,13,Fimmediately stepped in and worked
OL,14,Ftirelessly for several hours using
OL,15,Fspecialist cleaning materials to
OL,16,Fremove the graffiti before it could
OL,17,Fpermanently set.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,F"Their swift action prevented what
OL,7,Fcould have been significant and
OL,8,Flasting damage, although further
OL,9,Fpolishing and restoration work is
OL,10,Fstill required."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the 125 Group said:
OL,14,F"As a charity that relies on people's
OL,15,Fgenerosity and spare time to do what
OL,16,Fwe do, we're very grateful for the
OL,17,FEast Lancashire Railway volunteers for
OL,18,Ftheir speedy response to clear up this
OL,19,Fact of violence".
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,FMike Kelly, Chairman of the East
OL,7,FLancashire Railway, said:
OL,9,F"This is a disgraceful and deeply
OL,10,Ffrustrating attack on a railway run
OL,11,Flargely by volunteers, with many steam
OL,12,Fand diesel traction owned either by
OL,13,Fthe ELR or groups and in some cases,
OL,14,Fprivate individuals who give their
OL,15,Ftime freely to preserve our railway.
OL,16,FIt is nothing short of a kick in the
OL,17,Fteeth for those who work so hard to
OL,18,Fmaintain and preserve historic
OL,19,Ftraction and rolling stock.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,FWhat makes this even more infuriating
OL,7,Fis that this follows a similar
OL,8,Fincident less than 12 months ago, when
OL,9,Fnearly 30 glass panes across two
OL,10,Fcoaches were smashed, causing
OL,11,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage.
OL,13,FWe are working closely with the police
OL,14,Fand are determined to see those
OL,15,Fresponsible identified and held
OL,16,Faccountable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778166669
OL,3,CHeritage railway victim of 'mindless'
OL,4,Cvandalism attack
OL,6,FI want to place on record my sincere
OL,7,Fthanks to our outstanding volunteers,
OL,8,Fwhose immediate and determined
OL,9,Fresponse ensured the damage was
OL,10,Fcontained. Their commitment stands in
OL,11,Fstark contrast to the senseless
OL,12,Factions of those responsible."
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police attended the
OL,15,Fscene, gathered evidence, and have
OL,16,Fconfirmed that patrols in the area
OL,17,Fwill be stepped up. Anyone with
OL,18,Finformation about those responsible is
OL,19,Furged to contact Crimestoppers
OL,20,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111 or via
OL,21,Fcrimestoppers-uk.org.
OL,26,@tD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
